SRP (Philippine / typical market base price): Approx. ₱1,300,000 – ₱1,800,000 (Varies by trim and configuration)
SPECS:
Overall Dimensions (mm): 5,330 × 1,855 × 1,815 Wheelbase (mm): 3,085 Seating Capacity: 5
ENGINE / PERFORMANCE
Engine Options:
2.4 L 4-Cylinder Diesel
Maximum Output: 150 hp
Maximum Torque: 400 Nm
2.8 L 4-Cylinder Diesel (higher trims)
Maximum Output: 204 hp
Maximum Torque: 500 Nm
Transmission: 6-speed manual or 6-speed automatic (depending on variant) Drivetrain: 2WD or 4WD depending on trim
CAPACITY & CAPABILITIES
Towing Capacity: ~3,500–3,800 kg (depending on engine/trim)
Payload Capacity: ~1,000–1,200 kg
Fuel Tank Capacity: 80 L
INTERIOR / CABIN / SPACE
Seating: 5 (Double Cab)
Infotainment: 8” touchscreen, Apple CarPlay / Android Auto
Speakers: 4–6 (depending on variant)
CHASSIS / BRAKES / WHEELS / SUSPENSION
Front Brake / Rear Brake: Ventilated Discs / Drum or Disc (depends on variant)
Suspension: Double Wishbone front, Leaf Spring rear (standard 4WD setup)
Tires / Wheels: 265/65 R17 Alloy (standard), 18” wheels optional on higher trims
